      "span_text": "Injury Incidence Calculation and Statistical Analysis: Calculating incidence: 1) injury per activity (total number of injuries/number of activities), 2) injury per 1000 hours (1000 × total number of injuries / total activity hours), and 3) total activity hours (for match: 11 players × 1.5 hours; for training: number of players participating in the training × 1.5 hours). [CITATION_1]"
